---
import OriginMark from './OriginMark.astro';
---

<section id="manifesto" class="manifesto-section">
  <div class="manifesto-grid">
    <!-- Left Column: Geometry & Chapter ID -->
    <div class="manifesto-meta">
      <span class="manifesto-chapter">[ ETHOS 01 ]</span>
      <div class="manifesto-mark-wrapper">
        <OriginMark variant="gold" size={48} animate={false} />
      </div>
      <span class="manifesto-status">SYSTEM ANCHOR REGISTERED</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Narrative Preamble & Manifesto Copy -->
    <div class="manifesto-body">
      <h2 class="manifesto-heading">The Final Inch</h2>
      
      <p class="manifesto-preamble">
        You are standing at the final inch of a very long journey. You are no longer just a spectator; you are inside the origin.
      </p>

      <div class="manifesto-text-block">
        <p>
          Before there was a brand, before there was a product, there was a profound legacy of dignity and ecological intelligence.
        </p>
        <p>
          Consider a farmer who walks 12 kilometres into a forest. He picks what is ripe. He leaves what the animals took, because it was theirs. He leaves what the season hasn't finished. He carries back only what the forest agreed to give.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is not a sustainable farming practice or a certification. It is a decision made alone, 12 kilometres into the forest, with no observer. The product that arrives in your kitchen is the record of that decision.
        </p>
        <p>
          An origin is not a location. A location is a coordinate on a map, and a map is an abstraction.
        </p>
        <p>
          An origin is the living reality beneath the surface. It is the place — its altitude, its rainfall, its soil, its particular quality of morning light. The packet it comes in is not the product. It is the evidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="manifesto-link-block">
        <a href="/why" class="manifesto-read-btn">[ EXAMINE THE FOUNDING DOCUMENT ]</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto-section {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    background-color: var(--color-forest-deep);
    color: var(--color-warm-cream);
    padding: 12vh 8vw;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245, 237, 216, 0.1);
  }

  .manifesto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    gap: 8vw;
  }

  /* Left Column */
  .manifesto-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(245, 237, 216, 0.1);
    padding-right: 4vw;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 350px;
  }

  .manifesto-chapter {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .manifesto-mark-wrapper {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .manifesto-status {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(245, 237, 216, 0.35);
  }

  /* Right Column */
  .manifesto-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .manifesto-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .manifesto-preamble {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-warm-cream);
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .manifesto-text-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .manifesto-text-block p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-warm-cream);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .manifesto-link-block {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .manifesto-read-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-warm-cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 237, 216, 0.3);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .manifesto-read-btn:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
    background: rgba(166, 124, 60, 0.05);
  }

  /* Mobile responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .manifesto-section {
      padding: 8vh 6vw;
    }
    .manifesto-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .manifesto-meta {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245, 237, 216, 0.1);
      padding-right: 0;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      min-height: auto;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .manifesto-mark-wrapper {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .manifesto-status {
      display: none;
    }
    .manifesto-body {
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
